  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  THE FREQUENCY OF FREEDOM
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  There is a question that sits underneath all of the technical content in
  this documentation. It is not a question about antenna design or EARFCN
  allocation or PSS Zadoff-Chu sequences. It is a question about what kind
  of world we are building and what rights people have within it.

  We are building a world in which the electromagnetic environment is as
  consequential to daily life as the physical environment. The signals that
  move through the walls of your home affect your privacy, your security,
  your health, your finances, your location data, and the integrity of
  the devices you depend on. The decisions about who can transmit in that
  environment, at what power, on what frequencies, with what oversight,
  are decisions about power — about who gets to shape the invisible
  architecture that everyone inhabits.

  The right to breathe clean air was not always recognized as a right.
  The right to clean water was not always recognized as a right. The
  recognition of these rights required first that people understood they
  were being harmed, then that they had the means to document the harm,
  then that the documentation was sufficient to compel legal remedy.

  The right to inhabit a clean electromagnetic environment — free from
  unlicensed surveillance, free from forced device compromise, free from
  the broadcast of injurious signals into your body and your home without
  your knowledge or consent — is not yet recognized in those terms. But
  the harm is real. The technology to document it now exists. The legal
  framework, imperfect and incomplete as it is, provides mechanisms for
  remedy when evidence is presented.

  CTW SENTINEL is an instrument for seeing what would otherwise be
  invisible. What you do with what you see is yours to decide. But you
  cannot decide what you cannot see. And the first step toward any remedy
  is always documentation.

  See clearly. Document completely. Seek remedy through every channel
  available.

  The frequencies belong to everyone.


